# Number protection

- 9–10 digit runs stay grouped and copyable
- Do not weaken overlap/dedupe guards that protect phone/SSN sequences
- EN number-words → digits; do not break Spanish words that look like EN teens
- If unsure, add a failing test in `sensitiveDataProtector` tests before changing behavior
